{"tid":1417443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再理廢老！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:37:14.000Z","uid":201051,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4036e968c9841b0948529d134a5c25f81166d63c","tid":1417443,"uid":201051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"民意好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知大家遊行緊聽到廢老講鳩嘢好燥底<br />\n但係希望大家唔好理啲垃圾<br />\n冇人理佢佢就會自己收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日喺旺角見到幾個廢老<br />\n個個走去兇佢<br />\n我覺得冇呢個必要<br />\n仲有人影到喺其他示威地方有人背後打廢老一拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係割蓆<br />\n只係想大家諗吓自己嘅行動對民意有幾大影響<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ed1a37b06c8b2e372c86705a1e6fe045345fef8","tid":1417443,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:36:52.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a9942d6a9ec16b59269161395f02dda08800e6e","tid":1417443,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"再post: 文宣攻勢開始啦，打左啲野大家幫手spread啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}